paragraphs.text:
-- 活跃用户
-- 日期格式(如'20171218')
select
   summary.event_time_day,
   summary.group_wechat_id,
   summary.name,
   count(distinct summary.user_id)
from (
    select
        summary.app_id,
        summary.event_id,
        summary.event_time_day,
        summary.user_id,
        gu.group_wechat_id,
        g.name
    from fact_event_summary summary
    inner join dim_user_ids ids
        on ids.uid=summary.user_id
    inner join dim_group_user gu
        on gu.user_wechat_id=ids.wechat_id
    inner join dim_group g
        on g.wechat_id=gu.group_wechat_id
    where summary.app_id=1 and g.partner_id=1
) summary
where summary.event_time_day>=${开始日期} and summary.event_time_day<=${结束日期} and summary.app_id=1
group by summary.group_wechat_id,summary.name,summary.event_time_day
order by 1,3
;

paragraphs.text:
-- 活跃用户 deadletter
select
   summary.event_time_day,
   summary.group_wechat_id,
   summary.name,
   count(distinct summary.user_id)
from (
    select
        deadletter.app_id,
        deadletter.event_id,
        to_char(deadletter.event_time, 'yyyyMMdd') event_time_day,
        deadletter.user_id,
        gu.group_wechat_id,
        g.name
    from event_deadletter deadletter
    inner join dim_group_user gu
        on gu.user_wechat_id=deadletter.user_id
    inner join dim_group g
        on g.wechat_id=gu.group_wechat_id
    where deadletter.app_id=1 and g.partner_id=1
) summary
where summary.event_time_day>=${开始日期} and summary.event_time_day<=${结束日期} and summary.app_id=1
group by summary.group_wechat_id,summary.name,summary.event_time_day
order by 1,2
;
